## Update a user's password

Update a user's password

> Definition

```shell
PUT https://api.zoom.us/v2/users/{userId}/password
```

> Example Request

```shell
$ curl https://api.zoom.us/v2/users/{userId}/password \
   -d '{
    "password": "string"
}'
```

> Example Response

```text
204 No Content
```

